    "Furthermore, the research institutions behind the publications are the Chinese Academy of Sciences (357), Tsinghua University (314), and the Ministry of Education of the People's Republic of China (196), three of them from China as evidenced in Fig. 5.",
    "Moreover, the three funding sponsors behind publications on TM belong to China and the United States, National Natural Table 5 presents the most prolific authors in this field.",
    "Our results show that all prolific authors belong to the computer science subject area and majority are from China and the United States.",
    "The authors have published at least 33 TM research papers, and their h-index suggests the career stage of the authors, which seem to be mid or senior researchers in the area.",
    "H-indices in Scopus indicate a balance between the productivity (scholarly output) and citation impact (citation count) of a researcher's publications."
